{"word":"Reasoning","slug":"reasoning","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Reasoning</b> With God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=13&verse=3'>Job 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=13&verse=28'>Job 13:28</a><br/> God reasons with men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=11'>Exo 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=5'>Exo 20:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=11'>Exo 20:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=18'>Isa 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=4'>Isa 5:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=43&verse=26'>Isa 43:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=1'>Hos 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=2'>Mic 6:2</a><br/> Natural understanding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=36'>Dan 4:36</a><br/> To be applied to religion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=15'>1Co 10:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Pe 3:15</a><br/> Not a sufficient guide in human affairs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=8'>Deu 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=3&verse=5'>Pro 3:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=14&verse=12'>Pro 14:12</a><br/> Of the Pharisees<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=22'>Luk 5:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=20&verse=5'>Luk 20:5</a><br/> Of Paul from the scriptures<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=2'>Act 17:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=4'>Act 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19'>Act 19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=25'>Act 24:25</a><br/> The gospel cannot be explained by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=28'>1Co 1:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=2&verse=14'>1Co 2:14</a><br/><a href='S:Investigation'>Investigation</a>; <a href='S:Philosophy'>Philosophy</a>"}]}